Tapps undertakes to provide the necessary treatment of
personal information/data in compliance with the specific local laws of access
of its users, but is not responsible, under any circumstances, for the legal
treatment of information/data belonging to users who are located in
jurisdictions which do not offer a legislation for the legal treatment of
