use such notifications to remind you about your activities within the App. You
will receive push notifications only
if
you
are subscribed to such notifications in the App.
You can accept local notifications, but you may disable
these messages at any time by turning off the notifications from the “Options”
or “Settings” page within the Application.
We collect push
notifications tokens for us to be able to determine whether you are subscribed
to push notifications. When you decide to unsubscribe from push notifications,
such push notification tokens will be deleted from our database.”
